In this phase of the experiment, you will make similarity judgments for paintings you have encountered over the course of the experiment.

You will see a grid of 9 images on the screen. Click the two images that you believe look the most similar to the center image. Your first selection should be the image that you think looks most similar.

After you make your selection(s), a new display will be shown.

Be sure to consider all images carefully when you are making your choices.

Click "next" to begin the task.

You are halfway though this phase of the experiment. Please take a short break. You may step outside to stretch, use the restroom, or get a drink of water if you need to. If you choose to leave the room, please do so quietly so as not to distract other participants in the room.

After you take your break, please press the 'next' button below to begin the next section.

This is the final phase of the experiment. You will continue to make similarity judgments for paintings you have encountered over the course of the experiment, as you've done before.

You will see a grid of 9 images on the screen. Click the two images that you believe look the most similar to the center image. Your first selection should be the image that you think looks most similar.

After you make your selection(s), a new display will be shown.

Be sure to consider all images carefully when you are making your choices.

Click "next" to begin the task.
